name: 004 Lily
description:
Cryptotummys series
Mutated abandoned plushies
3024x4032
Lily was first found by three shepherd children by a tree right outside their town. The children described the plushie as "The One-eyed Angel" and believed the plushie was able to perform miracles. The whole town was together right in the center of town admiring, praying, and worshiping the plushie just as the first bomb of the big war hit.
The number of casualties is still disputed.
